'''Herman Nils Johansson''' (born 16 October 1997) is a Swedish professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[defender (association football)|defender]] for [[MLS]] club [[FC Dallas]] and the [[Sweden men's national football team|Sweden national team]].

==Club career==
In December 2020, Johansson was recruited by [[Mjällby AIF]], where he signed a three-year contract.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fotbollskanalen.se/allsvenskan/mjallby-varvar-mittfaltare-fran-ettan-hog-utvecklingspotential/|title=Mjällby värvar mittfältare från ettan: "Hög utvecklingspotential"|trans-title=Mjällby recruits midfielder from one: "High development potential"|language=sv|date=11 December 2020|author=Fredrik Andersson|website=fotbollskanalen.se|access-date=23 March 2022}}</ref>

In December 2025, Johansson was presented as a new player for [[FC Dallas]], a contract that extends through the 2028–29 season with an option for the 2029–30 season.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fcdallas.com/news/fc-dallas-signs-swedish-international-herman-johansson-from-mjallby-aif|title=FC Dallas Signs Swedish International Herman Johansson from Mjällby AIF|date=30 December 2025|website=www.fcdallas.com|access-date=31 December 2025}}</ref>

==International career==
In November 2025, Johansson received his first call up for [[Sweden men's national football team|Sweden]] to a [[2026 FIFA World Cup qualification|2026 World Cup qualification]] fixture against [[Slovenia men's national football team|Slovenia]], following an injury from [[Emil Holm (footballer)|Emil Holm]]. He made his debut against Slovenia on 18 November 2025, replacing [[Mattias Svanberg]] in the 65th minute of a 1–1 draw.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Herman Johansson kallas in|url=https://www.svenskfotboll.se/nyheter/landslag/2025/11/johansson-ersatter-holm/|access-date=16 November 2025 |website=www.svenskfotboll.se |language=sv}}</ref>

On 30 May 2026, Johansson was called up for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]], replacing injured [[Emil Holm (footballer)|Emil Holm]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.svenskfotboll.se/nyheter/landslag/2026/05/johansson-ersatter-holm/ |title=Herman Johansson ersätter Emil Holm |trans-title=Herman Johansson replaces Emil Holm |publisher=[[Swedish Football Association]] |date=May 30, 2026 |access-date=May 30, 2026 |language=sv}}</ref>

